											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="She shows us an old daguerrotype photo of two individuals: Ketheric Thorm and Aylin (Nightsong). They stand side-by-side in a somewhat austere way, rather than affectionate. Still, each has kindness in their face. Isobel was the (magical) &#xD;&#xA;photographer.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;" />
